text: "Satisfya" is a Punjabi hip-hop single by Imran Khan, released on 10 May 2013 by IK Records (Imran Khan). == Reception == As of 25 August 2020 song's music video has over 473 million+ views on YouTube. It is one of the most popular songs by Imran Khan. AsianImage described the song as catchy and motivational. == References == == External links == * Satisfya on Spotify * Satisfya on iTunes Category:2013 singles Category:Punjabi-language songs Category:Pakistani songs
